  m_text: 'From: Happiness Corp.

    To: Agent Love


    Great job Agent Love,
    the situation at the cafe looks to be under control.

    I wish I had better
    news for you, but we keep geting reports of disturbances in the city. We haven''t
    been able pin point the exact location, best if you go out there and look for
    yourself.


    Good luck and stay happy!

'
